 down the game to a crawl in order to select the next object with ease, and manipulate it with precision. In order to keep the game fun, there's no limit to how often you can use this mechanic.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524180/extras/e14e92c05bc2c86a8a425fb44523d77b.poster.avif?t=1702171478\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524180/extras/e14e92c05bc2c86a8a425fb44523d77b.webm?t=1702171478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524180/extras/e14e92c05bc2c86a8a425fb44523d77b.mp4?t=1702171478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Casual Gameplay</h2>Although some of the levels might pose a good challenge, this is a <strong>casual game</strong>. There is no pressure to complete every level and levels can be skipped at anytime via the level select. In addition to the ordinary level select there are also some extra-difficult bonus levels! Which can be unlocked after the ordinary levels for some additional challenge.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524180/extras/7b04599fc1d86b8649289f39cdf5fb31.poster.avif?t=1702171478\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524180/extras/7b04599fc1d86b8649289f39cdf5fb31.webm?t=1702171478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524180/extras/7b04599fc1d86b8649289f39cdf5fb31.mp4?t=1702171478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
